SUMMARY:[rollover] [easy win] Add Caddy basicauth to uzelhub-web preview
DESCRIPTION:Rolled forward from 2026-03-25. Add Caddy basic auth to the uzelhub-web preview — single shared credential for a small trusted circle.\n\nRepo: uzelhub-web\n\nInfrastructure:\n- Domain: Porkbun registered\n- DNS/proxy: Cloudflare (proxied)\n- Web server: Caddy on Hetzner VPS\n\nImplementation (~2 minutes):\n  1. Generate hash:  caddy hash-password\n  2. Add to Caddyfile:\n       preview.uzelhub.com {\n         basicauth {\n           uzel $2a$14$<hash>\n         }\n         root * /path/to/uzelhub-web\n         file_server\n       }\n  3. caddy reload\n  4. Test with incognito window\n\nUpgrade path: swap basicauth block for Cloudflare Access when per-user logins are needed.
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:task-settings-color-20260326@predictor_ingest
DTSTAMP:20260326T120000Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260326
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260327
SUMMARY:Fix filter/settings panel text color and inactive checkbox color
DESCRIPTION:Filter panel (right-side settings) has two CSS bugs in dark mode:\n\n1. .checkbox-label used color: var(--gray-700) which is NOT remapped in dark mode → dark text on dark background (invisible). Fixed by switching to var(--color-text-primary) which IS semantically overridden.\n\n2. Disabled/inactive type labels used Tailwind utility class text-gray-400 (not a semantic token\, doesn't adapt to theme). Fixed by introducing .checkbox-label--inactive using var(--color-text-tertiary).\n\nFiles changed:\n- web/css/components/input.css — new .checkbox-label--inactive variant\n- web/js/filter.js — disabled label class switched to checkbox-label--inactive\n\nStatus: COMMITTED on claude/review-daily-tasks-h4e9h — verify on next Cloudflare cache purge.
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR
